name: UIUCAlkemi
body:
### Welcome to UIUCAlkemi.

UIUCAlkemi is a collaboration between [Lawrence Livermore National Laboratory](https://www.llnl.gov/) and the [Department of Computer Science at the University of Illinois at Urbana Champaign](cs.illinois.edu). The goal of the collaboration is to produce a set of web-based tools for visualizing Machine Learning (ML) structures such as decision trees.

### Status
We are actively developing the toolset and will announce when an alpha release is available

### Authors and Contributors
